<%= @passenger.name %>'s Show Page

Passenger is flying on the following flights:
<% @passenger.flights.each do |flight| %>
  Flight#: <%= link_to flight.number, "/flights/#{flight.id}" %>
<% end %>

Add flight to passenger
<%= form_tag "/passengers/#{@passenger.id}/flight_passengers", method: :post do %>
  <%= label_tag :flight_number %>
  <%= text_field_tag :number %>

  <%= submit_tag "Submit" %>
<% end %>
